<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n01084a"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n01" href="#n01084a">N01 (VI.B.10)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n01all.htm#n01084a"> 84(a)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Chinese oath (blow out / lighted match</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[COCAINE TRAFFIC IN WEST END. / [&hellip;]</font> / NOVEL FORM OF OATH. / LIGHTED MATCH BLOWN OUT BEFORE EVIDENCE.] Fong was <font color="green">[&hellip;]</font> called. He said that he belonged to the &ldquo;<mark>Chinese</mark>&rdquo; religion. The Magistrate.&mdash;What <mark>oath</mark> is binding on him? <font color="green">[&hellip;]</font> The interpreter said <mark>a match should be lighted and blown out</mark>, and this form of oath was administered. <small> <a name="ES13nov22" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#ES13nov22"><cite title="source">Evening Standard</cite></a> (13 November 1922) 6/1</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Raphael transcription: <a name="c05146d" href="c05all.htm#c05146d">VI.C.05:146(d)</a> </mm></dd> </dd></dl>
